1. *Pitali* smo ga za njegove planove za budućnost. (We asked him about his plans for the future.)
2. *Pitala* sam ga o njegovom putovanju. (I asked him about his trip.)
3. *Pitali* smo ga da li je spreman da krene s nama. (We asked him if he was ready to go with us.)
4. *Pitali* smo ga o detaljima. (We asked him about the details.)
5. *Pitala* sam ga šta misli o tome. (I asked him what he thinks about it.)
6. *Pitali* smo ga o njegovom najdražem gradu. (We asked him about his favorite city.)